text:
That's a letter from the fans, right?
Is something up?

No, no matter how many times I read it, I just can't
get used to it... It's a mix of feeling happy, grateful....
every time, I wonder what I should do...

Just saying "I'll do my best"
feels inadequate, you know?

Yeah... but... I think it's okay not to force
yourself to come up with an answer.

Thanks, Producer.
I'll be right back!
